summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Parks and Recreation Department and the City Light Department; authorizing transfer of partial jurisdiction over certain City (Parks and Recreation Department) property within Carkeek Park in the southwest quarter of Section 25, Township 26 North, Range 3 East, W.M., in King County, Washington, to the City Light Department for overhead and underground electrical distribution purposes, (P.M. 260325-3-002).
